      "writtenOn": "2019-03-07T21:58:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "There are never supposed to be 2 pipes waiting for the snapshot response simultaneously. (There can be multiple open pipes, but only one of them can be waiting for a response at any time. Trying to trigger snapshots from 2 different threads is too dangerous.) I want to enforce this behavior, let me take a closer look and see what I can do.",
      "parentUuid": "b47183ae_e61f0fa7",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 269,
        "startChar": 4,
